HEADWORD: highjacking
<hw>highjacking</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The seizure of control of a
vehicle while it is in transit, either to rob it or divert it to an
alternate destination.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hijacking.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

